observe.desc:
-> [
{Figure is that of a skull with a crown of thorns, attached to a gigantic cross. It levitates about a meter above the ground.}
]

-> [
{Despite its harsh appearance, it hardly ever leads an attack. It often makes noises by clacking its teeth together but there is no need to pay extra attention to that noise. Stress levels rises rather sluggishly, so less attention is required compared to other Abnormalities. When stressed, ‘feeding’ it is necessary although it does not feed on typical sustenance.}
]

-> [
{It feeds on human ‘sins’, revealed through confession. Employee on duty must sit (or stand) in front of the creature and confess to his/her sins. There is no way to know how it digests words but stress levels do decrease.}
]

-> [
{When the confession is untrue, there is no telling what may happen.}
